---
const qaLogUrl =
  "https://github.com/sociotechnica-org/skillmaker-studio/tree/main/docs/phase20";

const rows = [
  { version: "as adopted", n: "3", passRate: "67%", ci: "[21%, 94%]", label: "below smoke" },
  { version: "v2 (revised)", n: "3", passRate: "100%", ci: "[44%, 100%]", label: "below smoke" },
];
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-3xl">
      What honest numbers look like
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-ink-dim leading-relaxed">
      We don&#39;t have customer logos to show you — pre-alpha, no customers yet.
      What we have is <a href={qaLogUrl} class="text-accent transition hover:text-accent-dim" rel="noreferrer">our own QA logs</a>:
      a hand-written skill adopted from a real repo, measured, revised, and
      measured again on claude-code.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 max-w-3xl overflow-x-auto rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface">
    <table class="w-full text-left text-sm">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-dim">
          <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">version</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">n</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">pass rate</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">95% ci</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">label</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {
          rows.map((row) => (
            <tr class="border-b border-border last:border-b-0">
              <td class="px-4 py-3 text-ink">{row.version}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-ink-dim">{row.n}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-ink">{row.passRate}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-ink-dim">{row.ci}</td>
              <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-ink-dim">{row.label}</td>
            </tr>
          ))
        }
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-dim">
      Both cells say &ldquo;below smoke&rdquo; because three runs is a sample, not a
      proof — the product refuses to let you over-trust the numbers, even when
      they flatter us. That refusal is the product.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
